csTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ylu1665702637742.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ylu1665702637742.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ylu1665702637742.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ylu1665702637742\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Selection Delay (\n                              SelectionDelay)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enables (or disables) a delay of 200 milliseconds before firing the valueChanged trigger in the Tree widget, when using keyboard navigation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_w891ab1b5b1_w892ab1b5_w893ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__p_d106889e1_d106890e1_d106891e1\">SelectionDelay=<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Tree widget fires the valueChanged trigger when a node has been selected for more than 200 milliseconds.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d12608e1_d12609e1_d12610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Tree widget fires the valueChanged trigger for every node it selects.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_wpb_gfk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884162e132\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_gfx_gfk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884162e178\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__p_d106898e1_d106899e1_d106900e1\">When using the keyboard to navigate through the\n            tree items, setting  SelectionDelay to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> ensures that the trigger is not fired before the user has\n            really selected an item. This behavior is similar to the Windows Explorer tree view.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__p_d106901e1_d106902e1_d106903e1\">In some circumstances, such as data entry via a\n            tree view, the delay may be undesirable. In this case, you can turn the delay off by\n            setting the  SelectionDelay property.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_xby_3fk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884162e197\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__p_d106907e1_d106908e1_d106909e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__pre_h2c_kfk_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"SelectionDelay=true\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__pre_gkj_4fk_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vProps = $fieldproperties(FLD1, \"selectiondelay\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_eh3_kfk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884162e232\">Setting in Initialization File</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__p_d106913e1_d106914e1_d106915e1\">You can set the default value for this widget\n            property in the application <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__pre_yzs_lfk_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[widgets]\nMyTree=utree(selectiondelay=false)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylu1665702637742__section_rqq_pfk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884162e248\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Selection Delay ( SelectionDelay) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Selection Delay ( SelectionDelay) Enables (or disables) a delay of 200 milliseconds before firing the valueChanged trigger in the Tree widget, when using keyboard navigation. SelectionDelay= True | False Value Description True The Tree widget fires the valueChanged trigger when a node has been selected for more than 200 milliseconds. False The Tree widget fires the valueChanged trigger for every node it selects. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description When using the keyboard to navigate through the tree items, setting SelectionDelay to True ensures that the trigger is not fired before the user has really selected an item. This behavior is similar to the Windows Explorer tree view. In some circumstances, such as data entry via a tree view, the delay may be undesirable. In this case, you can turn the delay off by setting the SelectionDelay property. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"SelectionDelay=true\" Copy vProps = $fieldproperties(FLD1, \"selectiondelay\") Copy Setting in Initialization File You can set the default value for this widget property in the application .ini file. For example: ;usys.ini [widgets] MyTree=utree(selectiondelay=false) Copy Applies To utree (Tree) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}